episodes_names: And you thought there is never a girl online?
I thought we couldn't play net games at school?
I thought net games and reality were different?
I thought her secret wasn't going to get out?
I thought reincarnating would give me my big chance?
I thought if I declared my love, I was sure to succeed?
I thought if I went to the beach, I would become a normie?
I thought I was giving up being a net game husband?
I thought if we stayed over, we would get along better?
I thought we would do our best at the cultural festival?
I thought we could win by delegating to others?
My net game wife is a girl online!
